In re Resignation of Underwood.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Underwood (1994), 68 Ohio St.3d 1211.]

(No. 93-2551 Submitted January 5, 1994 Decided January 6, 1994.)

On Affidavit of Resignation.

The resignation of Mell Gilbert Underwood, Jr. of New Lexington, Ohio, as an attorney, Registration No. 0021151, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
